Global ASL Antibody Market Insights
ASL Antibody Market size was valued at USD 1.25 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.55 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.5% from 2024 to 2030.

ASL Antibody Market Overview
The ASL Antibody market size is expected to reach USD 1.8 billion by 2027, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% during the forecast period. The increasing prevalence of autoimmune diseases, along with the rise in demand for diagnostic tools in clinical settings, has significantly contributed to this growth. ASL antibodies are essential in the diagnosis of autoimmune disorders, particularly in conditions like systemic lupus erythematosus (SLE). A growing focus on personalized medicine and advancements in technology to improve antibody detection methods are also driving the market forward.

